OL,5,G1715 FIFA WC2026: Brazil v Japan
OL,6,     FBrazil v Japan (Kick-off 6.00pm).
OL,7,     FCoverage of the round-of-32 match
OL,8,     Fat Houston Stadium in the USA.
OL,9,     FBrazil finished top of Group C on
OL,10,     Fgoal difference ahead of Morocco
OL,11,     Fafter picking up seven points
OL,12,     Facross their three group games.
OL,13,     FThey will face a Japan side that
OL,14,     Ffinished second in Group F behind
OL,15,     Fthe Netherlands, after they drew
OL,16,     F1-1 with Sweden who had to settle
OL,17,     Ffor third place. The Asian side
OL,18,     Fwere unbeaten across their three
OL,19,     Fgroup games, winning once after
OL,20,     Fhammering Tunisia 4-0 and drawing
OL,21,     Ftwice including a thrilling 2-2
OL,22,     Fdraw against the Netherlands
OL,23,Vppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
