OL,5,G2305 Unbelievable Moments Caught on
OL,6,G     Camera
OL,7,     FEyewitness footage filmed by
OL,8,     Fmembers of the public, who share
OL,9,     Ftheir memories of these
OL,10,     Fexperiences. This edition features
OL,11,     Fa kayaker who was trapped behind a
OL,12,     Fwaterfall in Mexico, a barber who
OL,13,     Fpulled a driver from a burning car
OL,14,     Fin Las Vegas, and a family who
OL,15,     Fnarrowly escaped a doomed ship in
OL,16,     FGreece. Plus, former downhill
OL,17,     Fmountain bike world champion Gee
OL,18,     FAtherton recalls a fall from a
OL,19,     Fmountain in Wales that nearly cost
OL,20,     Fhim his life. Narrated by Roger
OL,21,     FAllam
