OL,5,G0115 FIFA WC2026: Netherlands v Morocco
OL,6,     FNetherlands v Morocco (Kick-off
OL,7,     F2.00am). Coverage of the
OL,8,     Fround-of-32 match at Monterrey
OL,9,     FStadium in Mexico. The European
OL,10,     Fside made it through to this stage
OL,11,     Fafter they finished top of Group F
OL,12,     Fthanks to winning two and drawing
OL,13,     Fone of their three matches. 5-1
OL,14,     Fand 3-1 victories over Sweden and
OL,15,     FTunisia put them through after
OL,16,     Fthey drew 2-2 with Japan in their
OL,17,     Fopening match of the tournament.
OL,18,     FMorocco finished second in Group C
OL,19,     Fbehind five-time winners Brazil on
OL,20,     Fgoal difference, and beat Haiti
OL,21,     F4-2 in their final game to end
OL,22,     Ftheir group campaign on seven
OL,23,Vppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
